source.name: Change of Address Applications filed via the Internet
source.description: This dataset provides monthly volumes at the national level from federal fiscal year 2008 onwards for Internet Change of Address.  The dataset includes only Internet Change of Address transactions. It should be noted that, in addition to using our online Change of Address application, the public might change an address by calling our 800 number, visiting a field office, or mailing us the request.  This dataset pertains only to the online alternative.
